# Regenerable emitter output. `scripts/parity_suite.sh` compiles every
# PARITY_FILES `.py` to a sibling `.fk` in-place (python-compile) on each run,
# so a committed `.fk` is always overwritten before it is read — it has no
# live reader and dirties the worktree after every parity run. Ignore them so
# a parity run leaves the tree clean.
*.fk

# Keep the two `.fk` that are NOT regenerated by the suite:
#   - endpoint_lattice_stats_live.fk — no `.py` sibling (not regenerable)
#   - python_typeann_demo.fk — has a `.py` but it is not in PARITY_FILES,
#     so the suite never recreates it
# Any future hand-authored `.fk` (one with no PARITY_FILES `.py` driving it)
# needs its own `!` line here to stay tracked.
!endpoint_lattice_stats_live.fk
!python_typeann_demo.fk

# Keep the four transmuted-endpoint recipes the live API loads at request time
# (api/app/routers/utils.py → serve_via_kernel). These ARE regenerated by the
# parity suite from their `.py` twins, but they are the deployable artifact the
# prod kernel reads: Dockerfile.api copies them into the image so load_recipe
# resolves on disk and the endpoints serve kernel-side instead of degrading to
# python-fallback. The committed `.fk` is byte-identical to python-compile
# output, so a parity run regenerates the same bytes and leaves the tree clean.
!endpoint_coherence_weight_demo.fk
!endpoint_nodeid_distance_demo.fk
!endpoint_nodeid_compatibility_demo.fk
!endpoint_weighted_average_demo.fk
!endpoint_simpson_diversity_demo.fk
!endpoint_idea_score_demo.fk
!endpoint_marginal_cc_return_demo.fk
!endpoint_breath_balance_demo.fk
!endpoint_shannon_entropy_demo.fk
!endpoint_softmax_weights_demo.fk
!endpoint_cost_vector_demo.fk
!endpoint_value_vector_demo.fk
!endpoint_grounded_roi_demo.fk
!endpoint_idea_marginal_from_record_demo.fk
!endpoint_idea_grounding_summary_demo.fk
!endpoint_idea_grounded_cost_sum_demo.fk
!endpoint_grounded_cost_demo.fk
!endpoint_grounded_value_demo.fk
!endpoint_concept_match_score_demo.fk
!endpoint_tag_match_score_demo.fk
!endpoint_worldview_alignment_demo.fk
!endpoint_coherence_summary_score_demo.fk
